### II.5. The Linguistic Decay Function (Λ)

To quantify the transition from Level 7.1 to Level 8.0 instability, we utilize the **Linguistic Decay Function**.

In high-entropy environments, the "Semantic Floor" collapses as the ratio of adjectival density to causal anchors increases. We define the decay integral Λ as:

